<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Chronicles of Etheria</title>
    <style>
        /* 全局样式 - 星空背景 */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #0d1b2a, #1b263b, #415a77, #778da9);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 10s ease infinite;
        }

        /* 背景动画 */
        @@keyframes gradientBG {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        /* 星空粒子特效 */
        .stars {
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            background: url('https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/11/19/14/00/star-1837306_1280.jpg') repeat;
            opacity: 0.2;
            animation: starsMove 30s linear infinite;
        }

        @@keyframes starsMove {
            from { background-position: 0 0; }
            to { background-position: -1000px 1000px; }
        }

        /* 标题动态渐变 */
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f0f, #ff0, #0ff, #f0f);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            animation: glow 2s infinite alternate;
        }

        @@keyframes glow {
            from { text-shadow: 0 0 5px #fff; }
            to { text-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff0, 0 0 30px #f0f; }
        }

        /* 内容区 */
        .container {
            padding: 50px 10%;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
        }

        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* 角色介绍 */
        .character {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        .character:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        /* 返回主页按钮 */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #fff;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transform: scale(1.1);
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- 星空背景 -->
    <div class="stars"></div>

    <h1>The Chronicles of Etheria</h1>

    <div class="container">
        <p>
            In the ancient world of Etheria, where the skies shimmered with ethereal light and the land pulsed with arcane energy,
            five legendary beings shaped the destiny of all existence.
        </p>

        <div class="character"><strong>CHL, the Weaver of Shadows:</strong> Master of illusions and secrets, bending reality to his will.</div>
        <div class="character"><strong>WXY, the Stormcaller:</strong> Summons the fury of the heavens, commanding lightning and thunder.</div>
        <div class="character"><strong>WDS, the Architect of Time:</strong> Guardian of history, ensuring the balance between past and future.</div>
        <div class="character"><strong>YJ, the Flameborn Sage:</strong> Keeper of the eternal fire, forging weapons of unimaginable power.</div>
        <div class="character"><strong>LLX, the Celestial Wanderer:</strong> A traveler between dimensions, unlocking cosmic mysteries.</div>

        <p>
            A great calamity looms over Etheria. Only by uniting their powers can they restore harmony, but as the prophecy foretells:
            <i>“When the five awaken, the veil shall break… but will salvation come, or the end of all things?”</i>
        </p>

       <a class="btn" href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")">🏠 Home</a>


    </div>

</body>
</html>
